Kr2s2n2a  (IV)--a brother of the Andhra servant Balin (Balipuccaka-Vi. P.) who killed his master Ka1n2va Sus4arman and usurped the throne. After him, his brother Kr2s2n2a became king. His son was S4ri1 S4a1ntakarn2a, 1) Bha1. XII. 1. 23; Br. III. 74. 162; Vi. IV. 24. 44-5. who ruled for 18 years. 2) M. 273. 3. 

